35
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:24,360
Was he worried or did he laugh about it?

36
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:27,000
I think he's worried about me,

37
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,640
he doesn't worry about himself,

38
