64
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:03,200
in the hands of Mao

65
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,960
if there is ever going to be another revolution

66
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,120
it will be like the revolution that

67
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:14,160
